" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6caeb19ca0d3f849b158be3c251316a704ab4c51","tid":1537870,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f11a23f6d5a6bed75e4d36d7ad67fa571aca9f1","tid":1537870,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"［超長文］前線革命宣言：830隻狗係我地斬嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533987</a><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳否則香港會輸，香港需要盡快成立武裝組織"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新華社報導，中共中央總書記習近平3日上午在中央黨校（國家行政學院）中青年幹部培訓班開班式上發表講話，呼籲「發揚鬥爭精神，增強鬥爭本領」。<br />\n在這篇總結講話內容的2400多字新聞稿中，「鬥爭」一詞共出現56次。<br />\n習近平指，黨和國家的事業都是在鬥爭中產生、發展、壯大的，如今要實現偉大復興，就「必須進行偉大鬥爭」。<br />\n<br />\n鬥爭的方向，是「堅持中國共產黨領導和我國社會主義制度不動搖」，不得危害實現「兩個一百年」奮鬥目標和實現中華民族的偉大復興。<br />\n鬥爭的領域，覆蓋「經濟、政治、文化、社會、生態文明建設和國防和軍隊建設、港澳台工作、外交工作、黨的建設等方面」。<br />\n鬥爭的期限，「不是短期的而是長期的，至少要伴隨我們實現第二個百年奮鬥目標全過程」。（編注：第二個百年目標為，到中華人民共和國成立100年時&mdash;&mdash;即2049年，建成「富強民主文明和諧美麗的社會主義現代化國家」。）<br />\n<br />\n習近平還指出，在鬥爭過程中「要注重策略方法」，「合理選擇鬥爭方式、把握鬥爭火候，在原則問題上寸步不讓，在策略問題上靈活機動」。<br />\n習近平提出，「領導幹部要主動投身到各種鬥爭中去」，「要做敢於鬥爭、善於鬥爭的戰士」。<br />\n中共中央政治局常委、中央書記處書記王滬寧出席了開班式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20190904-morning-brief/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20190904-morning-brief%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3JMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=96c01212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20190904-morning-brief/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">孝順仔棋王你老豆當年俾人鬥成點呀？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n結果俾人鬥死咗</blockquote>佢老竇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioGGGQZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioGGGQZ.png&h=450a3735&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>唔知點解我覺得幅圖對五毛殺傷力頗大"},{"pid":"65a5cf08b3efd6c165469b0be8c67311aabae721","tid":1537870,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f55de70899bacb7a39fa97acb735a41a4053cf93","tid":1537870,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"03003f20d5d51f7907f0e32be1281f58ee0d7843","tid":1537870,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0936e90d4c3d5190705483eeeed04063e98ee8aa","tid":1537870,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>民主訴求，缺一不可；<br />\n<br />\n以眼還眼，鷹犬全鎖；<br />\n<br />\n有錯企定，即決勿拖！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=